%F A007953 a(A051885(n)) = n.
%F A007953 a(n) <= 9(log_10(n)+1). - _Stefan Steinerberger_, Mar 24 2006
%F A007953 From _Benoit Cloitre_, Dec 19 2002: (Start)
%F A007953 a(0) = 0, a(10n+i) = a(n) + i for 0 <= i <= 9.
%F A007953 a(n) = n - 9*(Sum_{k > 0} floor(n/10^k)) = n - 9*A054899(n). (End)
%F A007953 From _Hieronymus Fischer_, Jun 17 2007: (Start)
%F A007953 G.f. g(x) = Sum_{k > 0, (x^k - x^(k+10^k) - 9x^(10^k))/(1-x^(10^k))}/(1-x).
%F A007953 a(n) = n - 9*Sum_{10 <= k <= n} Sum_{j|k, j >= 10} floor(log_10(j)) - floor(log_10(j-1)). (End)
%F A007953 From _Hieronymus Fischer_, Jun 25 2007: (Start)
%F A007953 The g.f. can be expressed in terms of a Lambert series, in that g(x) = (x/(1-x) - 9*L[b(k)](x))/(1-x) where L[b(k)](x) = sum{k >= 0, b(k)*x^k/(1-x^k)} is a Lambert series with b(k) = 1, if k > 1 is a power of 10, else b(k) = 0.
%F A007953 G.f.: g(x) = (Sum_{k > 0} (1 - 9*c(k))*x^k)/(1-x), where c(k) = Sum_{j > 1, j|k} floor(log_10(j)) - floor(log_10(j-1)).
%F A007953 a(n) = n - 9*Sum_{0 < k <= floor(log_10(n))} a(floor(n/10^k))*10^(k-1). (End)
%F A007953 From _Hieronymus Fischer_, Oct 06 2007: (Start)
%F A007953 a(n) <= 9*(1 + floor(log_10(n))), equality holds for n = 10^m - 1, m > 0.
%F A007953 lim sup (a(n) - 9*log_10(n)) = 0 for n -> oo.
%F A007953 lim inf (a(n+1) - a(n) + 9*log_10(n)) = 1 for n -> oo. (End)
%F A007953 a(n) = A138530(n, 10) for n > 9. - _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Mar 26 2008
%F A007953 a(A058369(n)) = A004159(A058369(n)); a(A000290(n)) = A004159(n). - _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Apr 25 2009
%F A007953 a(n) mod 2 = A179081(n). - _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jun 28 2010
%F A007953 a(n) <= 9*log_10(n+1). - _Vladimir Shevelev_, Jun 01 2011
%F A007953 a(n) = a(n-1) + a(n-10) - a(n-11), for n < 100. - _Alexander R. Povolotsky_, Oct 09 2011
%F A007953 a(n) = Sum_{k >= 0} A031298(n, k). - _Philippe Deléham_, Oct 21 2011
%F A007953 a(n) = a(n mod b^k) + a(floor(n/b^k)), for all k >= 0. - _Hieronymus Fischer_, Mar 24 2014
%F A007953 Sum_{n>=1} a(n)/(n*(n+1)) = 10*log(10)/9 (Shallit, 1984). - _Amiram Eldar_, Jun 03 2021
